description:
This week Anna and Sim sit down with America’s tough guy and Anna’s next-door neighbor, Jeremy Renner (The Hurt Locker, Arrival, Avengers)! He gets the royal treatment at Imaginarium Studios where Hollywood legend Karen Sarducci pitches projects to him with heavy Oscar buzz. They also talk about the realities of fame and what's it's really like to be a working actor! Afterward, the gang calls Kelsey, who needs advice on how to survive the holidays with a mother in law who doesn’t like her, and Laura, who’s boyfriend really loves football, maybe even a little too much.

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
